            "answer_text": "\u201cMongoloid\u201d is one classification used when the concept of race was first proposed as a scientific concept. That racial classification ( Caucasoid, Mongoloid, Negroid) was scrapped when genetics was incorporated into the study of human biology. There are no races within the human species. ",
